{"title":"金缕曲","authors":["赵树理"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":5,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金缕曲＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵树理遗作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁历翻新页。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜回头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年经过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇峰千迭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁臂银锄高下午，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改变乾坤陈设。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山飞水越。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处红旗赶大寨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洋溢乎中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满腔热。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神州豪气多风发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任凭他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷天雪乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压城云黑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举大旗红浪涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少雷锋、王杰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开万世，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太平事业。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宇宙无穷无尽愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿征程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋翼冲天阙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射白虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揽明月！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据赵树理同志的亲属记忆，此词写于一九六五年初。原词无标题，词牌名为编者所加。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔原载《诗刊》第五期〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}